              "content": "=Podcast: {{ $('HTTP Request1').item.json.title }}\nChannel: {{ $('HTTP Request1').item.json.author_name }}\n\nTranscript:\n{{ $('HTTP Request').item.json.content.slice(0, 12000) }}\n\nReturn EXACTLY this format:\n\n🎙 [Podcast Title]\n👤 [Host] x [Guest] — [Topic in 5 words]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n🧩 WHAT THIS CONVERSATION IS REALLY ABOUT\n[2 sentences. Not what the title says — what they actually spent most time on]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n❓ KEY QUESTIONS DISCUSSED\n[List the actual questions the host asked that drove the conversation. Be specific.]\n\nQ: [exact topic of question]\n→ [guest's actual answer in 1-2 lines. Use their words, their numbers, their claims]\n\nQ: [exact topic of question]\n→ [guest's actual answer in 1-2 lines]\n\nQ: [exact topic of question]\n→ [guest's actual answer in 1-2 lines]\n\n[max 6 questions — only the ones that had a real meaty answer]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n💎 HIGHLIGHTS WORTH REMEMBERING\n[Max 4 points. Only things that are specific, surprising, or non-obvious. No generic statements. Must include actual claims, numbers, or names from the podcast.]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n🔥 CONTROVERSIAL OR STRONG OPINIONS\n[Only include this section if the guest said something bold, unpopular, or that challenges mainstream thinking. Quote their actual stance. If nothing controversial was said, write: Nothing controversial in this one.]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n⚡ ONE LINE VERDICT\n[Would you recommend this podcast and why — brutally honest, one sentence]"
            }
          ]
